This is the Debian Linux prepackaged version of Sendmail, a complex mail
transport agent.

This package was put together by Robert Leslie <rob@mars.org> with sources
obtained from:
  ftp://ftp.sendmail.org/pub/sendmail/

The following copyright applies to this software:

  Copyright (c) 1983, 1995 Eric P. Allman
  Copyright (c) 1988 The Regents of the University of California.

Further copyright information can be found in the file /usr/doc/copyright/BSD
on Debian systems.
